sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend as React SPA
    participant Backend as FastAPI
    participant Worker as Celery Worker
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Qdrant as Qdrant

    User->>Frontend: Upload image + metadata
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/v1/images
    Backend->>DB: INSERT images, segments
    DB-->>Backend: image_id, segment_ids
    Backend->>Worker: enqueue segmentation job
    Worker->>DB: UPDATE segments (bbox, crop_path)
    Worker-->>Backend: segmentation complete

    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/v1/retrieval
    Backend->>Worker: enqueue feature extraction
    Worker->>Qdrant: KNN search (cosine, top-K)
    Qdrant-->>Worker: neighbor vector + payload
    Worker->>DB: INSERT retrieval_results + neighbors
    Worker-->>Backend: job complete

    Backend->>DB: SELECT ranked species results
    DB-->>Backend: scores, neighbor metadata
    Backend-->>Frontend: species ranking + evidence
    Frontend-->>User: Display results + neighbor thumbnails
